Algorithm for ATM MACHINE

Step1- Walk to the ATM 
Step2- Insert ATM card
Step3- Select preffered language
Step4- Enter ATM pin 
Step5- Select withdrawal choice
Step6- Select account type
Step7- Enter the amount to withdraw
Step8- Collect cash from the ATM slot
Step9- Stop transaction
Step10- Take ATM card

INPUTED DATAS
1. ATM Card
2. ATM PIN
3. Amount of cash
4. Yes/No intructions

DECISIONS
1. If ATM card is in good condition to run transaction
2. Validity of ATM card Pin 
3. Comparing the amount in the account with withdrawal amount, then make decision to dispense or not.

POSSIBLE OUTPUTS
1. Validity of informations and datas
2. Dispensing of cash
3. Rejection/dispensing of ATM Card

               
